      <title>Olsen Bicentennial Professor</title>
      <link>//uvasrg.github.io/olsen-bicentennial-professor/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Sep 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>//uvasrg.github.io/olsen-bicentennial-professor/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m honored to have been elected the &amp;ldquo;Olsen Bicentennial Professor of Engineering&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The appointment is in the 12 Septemember 2025 &lt;a href=&#34;https://bov.virginia.edu/sites/bov/files/2025-10/%2725%20SEPTEMBER%2011-12%20FULL%20BOARD%20MINUTES.pdf&#34;&gt;Board of Visitors minutes&lt;/a&gt; (page 13072):&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;center&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;//uvasrg.github.io/images/bov-excerpt1.png&#34; width=&#34;90%&#34; alt=&#34;RESOLVED, the actions relating to the chairholders are approved as shown below:&#34;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;//uvasrg.github.io/images/bov-excerpt2.png&#34; width=&#34;90%&#34; alt=&#34;David E. Evans, as Olsen Bicentennial Professor of Engineering, for the periodAugust 25, 2025 through August 24, 2030. Evans will continue as Professor of Computer&#xA;Science, without term.&#34;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;/center&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The professorship was created by a gift from Greg Olsen in 2019 to celebrate the bicentennial of the University&amp;rsquo;s founding in 1819:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
